The '''Early Access Release''' of [[V Rising]] (version 0.5.41188, May 17, 2022) launched the game on Steam Early Access with the biomes [[Farbane Woods]], [[Dunley Farmlands]], [[Hallowed Mountains]], [[Silverlight Hills]] and [[Cursed Forest]]. Seventeen numbered hotfixes shipped during the 0.5 era — see the [[Patch Notes]] index for the individual Steam announcements.

